{
  "stem": "150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, depending on what you did, you would get five [GERMAN] or 10 [GERMAN] or 15, or whatever. 20, 25, you'd probably die, because--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, when I got beaten up?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I was never whipped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I just got hit in the face or over the back by a kapo and all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you know, when I didn't move fast enough, or if I just was a little bit late taking off my hat before-- any time you saw a German, you were supposed to snap to attention one meter away, take off your hat, and say, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Prisoner 82191, at your order, sir.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was powerless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father, who was the most powerful figure in my world, couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was pitiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was just as angry as I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I still remember what a shock it was to me-- my father smoked before the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he gave it up on doctor's orders before we went into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at one point towards the very end of the war, maybe a month before the end of the war, we got Red Cross packages, which was totally unexpected.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't-- I don't know how it happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, they cheated even on that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They brought in the packages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they gave one pack-- one package for two people to be divided.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was like a gift from heaven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The packages had a can of sardines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it had a package, a packet, maybe half a powder or a quarter pound of cubed sugar, and it had two packs of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I don't remember what else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think that's all it had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And people divided.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the sugar was just great.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
